                <span class="tour-card-badge">VIP</span>
                <img src="kota.jpg" alt="น้ำตกโคทะ" style="width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 300px; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 1rem;" onerror="this.style.display='none';">
                <h4 class="tour-card-title">🏆 VIP ทีลอซู-โคทะ 1 วัน</h4>
